# CJ → eBay USA — corrida manual 3E.4 (REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP / similar)
# NO ejecutar en bloque sin revisar: implica costes reales en CJ/eBay cuando el operador dispare los pasos.
#
# Placeholders:
#   {{baseUrl}}     ej. http://localhost:3000
#   {{token}}       JWT del usuario operador
#   {{ebayOrderId}} id de orden en eBay (fulfillment)
#   {{orderId}}     id interno devuelto por import (cj_ebay_orders.id)
#
# Orden operativo recomendado:
#   1) system-readiness (sin llamadas externas)
#   2) config (opcional)
#   3) import
#   4) operational-flow
#   5) place → confirm → pay (si MANUAL)
#   6) status (poll)
#   7) sync-tracking (cuando haya tracking)
#   8) evidence-summary (export / plantilla)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_HERE
@ebayOrderId = EBAY_ORDER_ID_HERE
@orderId = INTERNAL_CJ_EBAY_ORDER_ID_HERE

### 0 — Preparación (sin CJ/eBay HTTP)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/system-readiness
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1 — Config (opcional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1b — Forzar checkout manual (opcional)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/config
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {"cjPostCreateCheckoutMode": "MANUAL"}

### 2 — Importar orden eBay
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ebayOrderId": "{{ebayOrderId}}"
}

### 3 — Inspección de gates (solo DB)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/operational-flow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4 — Place (createOrderV2 payType=3) — REAL CJ
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/place
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 5 — Confirm — REAL CJ
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 6 — Pay balance — REAL CJ
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7 — Estado CJ (getOrderDetail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8 — Sync tracking (+ submit eBay si aplica) — REAL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/sync-tracking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 9 — Resumen evidencia (sanitizado, solo DB)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}/evidence-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10 — Detalle orden local (incluye buyerPayload; no usar en evidencia pública)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cj-ebay/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
